Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.82,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:9989,13826}I can feel the sunshine on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:17.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:13826,17121}I think I'll bask in it a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:22.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:18122,22126}It's a beginning of a new day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:28.46,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25338,28466}That's the moment I like the most,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:33.51,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29342,33513}the one that starts it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.84,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:33513,36849}Something lovely is about to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:40.72,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:36849,40728}I just have a hunch like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:48.40,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:40728,48403}Woom! My reflection the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:52.28,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:48403,52282}Woom! Looks rather pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:56.03,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:52282,56035}It feels so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:02.87,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56035,62875}I reach out to the clear blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:10.67,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:63793,70675}I'm so excited and filled with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:15.09,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:71467,75096}Love, work, everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.60,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:75096,78600}I want to take these challenges on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:24.89,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:78600,84897}and build myself again.
Comment: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:95116,95116}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:41.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100288,101497}{\i1}Your attention, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:48.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101497,108087}{\i1}This plane will be landing within 20 minutes\Nat the New Tokyo International Airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:54.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111549,114010}Who's that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:56.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114177,116804}Tomoko Nagata.\NShe's 28 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:58.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116804,118765}A successful detective\Nactive in the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:04.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119557,124187}She's so good that she solved a case\Nwhich even the FBI couldn't solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:07.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:124562,127774}So why do we have to meet her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:10.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128149,130777}The Mayor himself invited her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:14.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130777,134989}This means you may finally lose\Nyour job investigating St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:22.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138660,142372}She must be a very old-fashioned,\Nhomely and unpleasant woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:24.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142372,144415}I'm sorry for being\Nsuch an unpleasant woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:42.72,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:158680,162725}Phantasmal Masterpiece!\NA Woman Detective is Back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:46.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163059,166688}Do you know about\Nthe mysterious thief St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:52.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166938,172026}She uses magic freely and she sends\Na warning note prior to her crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:55.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172026,175446}No one knows her identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:56.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175446,176239}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:57.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176406,177365}Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177365,179200}This makes it all the easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:03.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179200,183162}I want to ask you for your\Nassistance in catching St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:07.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183162,187208}I've assured you that I'll catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:12.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187208,192338}Yes. I expect you can\Ncatch her someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:19.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193840,199095}But in this case, I think\Nit's better to ask this lovely lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:25.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201514,205977}I'm sorry, but I came back to Japan\Non a personal matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206185,207979}Can you make any\Narrangements to help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:29.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207979,209105}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:33.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211941,213568}To-mo-ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:37.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215486,217488}I can give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:40.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217488,220700}I'm sorry that I can't assist you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:43.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222118,223536}That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:46.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223536,226706}I definitely will\Narrest St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226706,228916}I'm the person who will catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:51.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228916,231419}Be quiet! This kind\Nof thing is done by age.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:53.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231419,233921}That's unfair! All of a sudden\Nyou're motivated!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:59.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234589,239385}Tomoko has sparked\Nthe detective fire in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239761,241512}It's nice to see a father\Nand son together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:05.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241512,245099}By the way, Asuka Jr.,\Nyou go to St. Paulia's, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245266,247185}What? How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247852,249187}Your uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249479,251773}Say, could you show me\Naround the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:13.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252440,253483}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:21.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255943,261199}The graph for y=2x is a straight line\Nwhich runs through the origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262033,264577}I wonder what\Nhappened to Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264577,266954}He's healthy and has\Nnever missed any classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:31.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267747,271876}According to Takamiya,\Nhe was summoned by the Mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:34.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271876,274128}That means it must have\Nsomething to do with St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:41.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277215,281302}Hey, Asuka Jr. is walking with\Na really beautiful woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:42.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281469,282678}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285056,286182}She's really beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:49.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286182,289685}I didn't know that\Nhe liked older women.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:52.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289977,292522}What's going on?\NGo back to your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292522,294565}Oh, Nagata?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:57.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295149,297068}Do you know her, Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:05:01.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297318,301489}Yes. She was the smartest student\Nin the history of this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:04.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301489,304617}If I remember correctly, she went\Nto a college in the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:10.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309247,310873}Do you know about her, Seira?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310873,312458}I've heard rumors about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:15.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312458,315628}She was the famous daughter\Nof a rich family in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:19.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315962,319715}On the hill from where you can see the port,\Nthere is a big European-style house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:21.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320216,321676}You mean that haunted house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:24.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321968,324428}Yes. She used to live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:28.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324428,328391}But the people who lived there\Nare missing, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328391,330434}That's the rumor, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:34.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331185,334897}I've heard she's\Na famous detective now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:37.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334897,337108}What?! A detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:47.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344031,347869}Just beyond here, I've found\Na really cute trinket store.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:49.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347869,349495}Let's go, Meimi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:51.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349704,351539}Yeah, but I have homework…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:54.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351539,354458}Just a little peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:57.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356210,357837}Oh, it's Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:59.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357837,359547}I wonder where she's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:00.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359547,360798}Let's follow her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:02.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360798,362633}What?! But…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:04.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362633,364886}– Don't worry!\N– Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369599,370850}Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371851,373853}Isn't this the haunted house?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:18.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374353,378441}I've heard that a first-year student in our school\Nheard a woman crying in the middle of night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:19.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378441,379567}Ryoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:29.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388075,389452}We met earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:31.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390286,391162}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391871,394206}Tomoko Nagata.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:36.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394206,396125}Yes. I'm Meimi Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:39.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397752,399879}A delicate and beautiful hand…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:43.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399879,403090}People who have hands like this\Nare often magicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406052,407470}Would you like to come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:48.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407470,408179}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409972,411140}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:02.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418230,422526}A lot of my memories are from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:05.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422526,425821}In your eyes, this must\Nbe like a haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:07.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425821,427156}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:09.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427156,429492}They were understanding parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:14.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429492,434246}When I said I wanted to study abroad,\Nthey let me do it without saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:14.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434246,434789}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:19.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437667,439251}Let's go upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:25.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443673,445216}It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:29.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446801,449220}I was always dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:30.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449220,450930}From this place…\NFrom this window.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:34.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452098,454392}I wanted to fly away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:36.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454392,456602}I wanted to go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:40.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457019,460815}I didn't notice\Nmy parents' love for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461273,463776}Your parents are…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463776,465736}Missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:47.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465736,467405}Since I went abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467905,469490}Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:52.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469490,472660}There's no reason\Nto tell you these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:53.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472660,473869}Please forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482169,483421}Excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:06.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483421,486549}I'm sorry I came in without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:08.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486549,488009}It brought back\Na lot of memories, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:09.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488509,489885}Please stay as long as you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:14.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490386,494348}To tell you the truth,\NI don't deserve to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:17.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494348,497059}Well, would you like to tell me why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:20.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499478,500771}Revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:22.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501022,502523}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:25.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502523,505317}The person who is responsible\Nfor my parents' disappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:27.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505317,507737}I only came back here\Nto get my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:31.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508279,511782}My parents were\Nart dealers in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512116,513534}Art dealers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:36.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513534,516245}Those people who sell pieces of art?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516537,517538}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:47.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524628,527256}My father was\Nstrict but affectionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:49.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527256,529633}Mother was always\Nwatching over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:52.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530259,532553}I was really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:58.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532553,538768}The piece of art my parents treasured most\Nwas a picture titled "Wings of Freedom".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:03.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538768,543314}But one day, a man\Nwho wanted it appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:05.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543814,545775}Of course, my parents\Nturned down his offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:11.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546984,551781}But in the end, they gave in to his enthusiasm\Nand they decided to sell it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:14.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551781,554366}My father though that\Nhe would treasure the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:18.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554366,558162}But the man betrayed\Nmy father's trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:23.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559371,563876}He said the picture he bought was\Na fake and he sued my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:24.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563876,564627}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:29.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565127,569090}Because my father didn't have\Nany evidence to prove otherwise,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:32.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569090,572093}he had to pay a lot\Nof money and apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:37.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572093,577306}Because of that he lost credibility\Nas an art dealer and he lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:39.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:577306,579100}That's why they disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:44.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579683,584355}As I was abroad,\NI didn't know what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:47.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:584355,587191}But I have always believed\Nthat my parents were innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:54.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589485,594698}But I didn't know what I could do\Nin order to prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:55.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594698,595908}That's why you became a detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:10:01.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596992,601288}In order to become strong and take revenge,\NI endured the most difficult training.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:10.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606335,610214}I continued to investigate the man\Nwho deceived my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:13.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611590,613175}And the man is…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:17.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614218,617346}He's the owner of Sugawara Industries,\NRyosuke Sugawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618264,620432}She's going to steal?!\NNo way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:25.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620724,625980}If she can prove that Sugawara\Nhas the real "Wings of Freedom",
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:29.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625980,629942}then she can prove\Nher parents' innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629942,632570}No! She shouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:33.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632570,633821}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633821,635948}I'll steal the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:41.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635948,641328}I'll steal it before Tomoko can\Nand reveal Sugawara's crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:45.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642037,645583}Her revenge is meaningless.\NI can't let her do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:58.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654884,658679}Today I'd like to take you around,\Naway from the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:10:59.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658679,659763}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:04.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661932,664059}I don't think you've seen enough\Nwith this boy as a guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:07.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664059,667062}This time I'd like to show you\Nan adult's hospitality!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:26.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681118,686248}"I'm taking {\i1}Wings of Freedom{\i0} that's in the\Npossession of Mr. Ryosuke Sugawara. – St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:28.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686582,688709}– She is…\N– What's that?
Comment: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:32.71,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:692713,692713}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:37.71,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:697718,697718}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:42.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698135,702389}The real "Wings of Freedom" is in\Nmy possession? Is that what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702389,703515}You don't have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:45.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704183,705392}That's silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:49.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705392,709146}I've always wanted that piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:52.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709146,712483}Because of that,\NI once bought a counterfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:56.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714318,716570}So you're saying you don't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:59.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716570,719365}Of course I don't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:03.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719365,723702}I'm the one who wants\Nto know where it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:08.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724328,728832}I've heard of\Nthe mysterious thief St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728832,730918}She must have\Nmisunderstood something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:12.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731460,732836}She is…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:17.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732836,737091}It's not like St. Tail to send\Nan inaccurate warning note.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:20.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737091,740511}You believe that petty thief's words?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:22.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740511,742388}She isn't a petty thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:26.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744098,746684}What Asuka Jr. said is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:32.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746684,752481}According to my research, St. Tail has\Nnever sent an inaccurate warning note.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:33.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752481,753607}Not even once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:37.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754066,757653}If you let us search your house,\Nwe can clear this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:39.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757861,759571}I must refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:40.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759571,760906}Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:44.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760906,764535}If you haven't done anything wrong,\Nit shouldn't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:46.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764535,766203}Because it isn't necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766203,767579}You don't even have any evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:52.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769873,772418}Chairman. It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:53.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772418,773711}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:54.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773711,774837}Detective Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:58.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774837,778173}I'll listen to your advice\Nand will let you guard the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:00.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778465,780009}Then we'll do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781218,783470}Isn't she that art dealer's daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:07.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783929,787224}Yes. I had it confirmed through\Nan American detective agency
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:09.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787224,789059}and there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:11.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789059,791687}Apparently she's been\Ninvestigating you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:12.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791854,792938}This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:15.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792938,795941}If she finds out\NI have the real picture, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:16.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795941,796650}Then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:19.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796942,799111}You don't even need to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799403,800612}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:27.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803115,807328}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:33.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811999,813334}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815419,817004}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:41.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818672,821633}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:56.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834646,836523}Be careful, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:59.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836523,839276}We don't know\Nwhat Tomoko will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839610,841904}Don't worry! It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:07.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844114,847826}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:14.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851955,854249}Asuka Jr., where is Detective Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:17.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854249,857127}He told me he had something\Nhe needed to check…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:20.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857836,860631}{\i1}What is he going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:37.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875396,877940}{\i1}I suppose she gave up…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880401,882403}Pretty impressive, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:53.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890953,893872}{\i1}I can't let you interfere\Nwith my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:58.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897418,898377}Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:14:59.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898377,899670}She's up in this tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:01.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899670,901588}Oh, no! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:08.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907052,908262}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:10.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908262,910722}Darn it! Never mind!\NLet's move in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:11.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910722,911682}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:16.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914810,916145}{\i1}What shall I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921608,923068}What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:31.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928323,931910}{\i1}You saved me!\NThank you, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:03.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960939,963942}This is the "Wings of Freedom"\Nyou were looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963942,965360}The real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:08.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965694,968280}It's the one your father sold to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:11.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968280,971325}I prepared the counterfeit\Nand switched them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:14.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971825,974119}Now that you've seen the picture\Nyou were looking for,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:16.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974119,976288}you don't have any regrets, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:18.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976955,978499}The one who broke in\Nshould have been St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:23.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978499,983253}So, even if you disappear,\Nno one will suspect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:28.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983879,988842}After the police leave,\NI'll decide how you should disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:35.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993597,995974}We've made the police leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:38.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995974,998143}But the media is making a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:42.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998393,1002105}I guess it would be better\Nto give them an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002105,1003482}Let's have a press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004983,1006068}This must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010489,1012199}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:56.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015953,1016995}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:59.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016995,1019373}You know that I set you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028840,1030008}{\i1}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:12.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030801,1032970}Let go! Let go of my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:14.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032970,1034012}Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:16.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034346,1036974}{\i1}I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:23.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041520,1043272}You almost did it, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043939,1045232}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:33.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052030,1053365}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:36.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053615,1056285}I'm sorry, but I can't\Ngive this picture to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:39.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057995,1059162}Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:42.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059162,1062332}You shouldn't steal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:43.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062332,1063125}Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065085,1067129}Asuka Jr.!\NWhere are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:48.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067129,1068880}Over here! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:12.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091111,1092112}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:15.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093196,1095657}Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:18.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096658,1098410}Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117638,1119222}Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:51.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126396,1131234}A thief by the name of St. Tail\Nseems to have been misinformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:54.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131234,1134363}I've been a victim,\Nboth six years ago and today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:58.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135322,1138200}You don't really have\N"Wings of Freedom", do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:18:59.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138575,1139826}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:04.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139826,1144790}If you have any doubt, please go ahead\Nand search my house or my company.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:14.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150671,1154049}That's a nice touch, Tajima…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:21.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157135,1161848}I, Ryosuke Sugawara,\Nswear to God that I am innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:30.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167521,1170107}It's the real "Wings of Freedom"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:35.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171733,1175028}– What?!\N– Please explain this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:37.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175028,1177322}I don't know!\NI don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177322,1178532}Mr. Sugawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:41.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179741,1181410}Please come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:44.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181868,1184871}Have you discussed this\Nwith the Mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:48.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185247,1188333}Maybe you should have\Na discussion with your conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:53.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190210,1193213}We've uncovered\Na few things about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:55.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193213,1195799}The materials she\Ngave us helped a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:59.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196341,1199261}You'll have a lot of time\Nto tell us your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:04.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201930,1204307}{\i1}Thank you, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:11.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206977,1211440}I heard that Sugawara\Nadmitted deceiving your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:13.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211440,1213150}My dad was quite pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:15.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213483,1215152}Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:17.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215152,1217654}Please thank your father for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:18.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217654,1218572}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:21.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219990,1221491}Haneoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:39.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238008,1239342}Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:41.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239342,1241887}I'll be cheering for you from America.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244848,1246933}What's the connection\Nbetween you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:48.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246933,1248935}We're best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1249603,1251313}I didn't know… Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:53.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251438,1253774}You're a guy.\NYou wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:55.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253774,1255942}Wait! Hey, Haneoka!
